==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water can
<hw>Wa"ter can`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Any one of
several species of Nuphar; the yellow frog lily; -- so called from the
shape of the seed vessel. See <er>Nuphar</er>, and cf.
<er>Candock</er>.</def> <rj><au>Dr. Prior.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water canker</ent>⟦br⟧
